23:48.160 --> 23:50.929 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But what we don't know is
whether this is
just posturing or whether this
is a policy

23:50.963 --> 23:52.131 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
