be part of a broader negotiation
with China

24:58.364 --> 25:01.033 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
about a whole series of economic
and foreign
policy issues.

25:01.066 --> 25:04.069 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
So, we just don't really know
what exactly
they're planing to do with this.

25:04.103 --> 25:05.304 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Was it just about Taiwan?

25:05.337 --> 25:07.706 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Is it just because they want to
push back
a bit on Taiwan?

25:07.740 --> 25:11.510 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
