leverage for a whole series of
other issues

25:11.543 --> 25:14.646 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
on the currency, on tariffs, on
the South
China Sea?

25:14.680 --> 25:15.647 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
It's unclear.

25:15.681 --> 25:16.648 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
