25:20.652 --> 25:22.454 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
KAREN TUMULTY, The Washington
Post: Well,
I think that Donald Trump, how
many times

25:22.488 --> 25:26.325 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
