32:32.117 --> 32:37.389 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The first foreign leader to call
president-elect
Trump after his victory was
Egypt's president,

32:37.422 --> 32:39.157 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
Abdel Fattah El-Sisi.

32:39.191 --> 32:44.262 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
