whether it's
in demonstrating without
necessary permits,

37:11.796 --> 37:20.472 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
in violent activity during
demonstrations,
and such issues that are
penalized in the

37:20.505 --> 37:21.473 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
