Egypt send some
to help him?

37:59.644 --> 38:01.446 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
SAMEH SHOUKRY: Categorically
not.

38:01.479 --> 38:06.317 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
Let me clarify that the
president, when he
made his statements, wasn't
referring to Syria

38:06.351 --> 38:08.153 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
